name: Edelweiss Air Airbus A340-300 Dusk Takeoff from Calgary Airport
description:
Edelweiss Air is by far my favourite summer seasonal visitor! With all the 787s and A330s that Calgary sees, their A340 certainly stands out. Here we have HB-JME departing Calgary for Zurich a little over a month ago, just after sunset. Their final flight for the season is fast approaching, in just a week from now. Can't wait to see them back next year! ATC is included, hope you enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
